Package com.peyrona.mingle.glue.gswing

Class GTableModel<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • com.peyrona.mingle.glue.gswing.GTableModel<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of objects stored in this table model
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
    public abstract class GTableModel<T>
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
    A generic table model that inserts new rows at the beginning and supports maximum row limits and filtering.

    This abstract table model provides functionality to:

    • Insert new rows at the top of the table (most recent first)
    • Limit the maximum number of rows to prevent memory issues
    • Filter rows based on a predicate function
    • Thread-safe operations for concurrent access
